<h3 class="sub-heading">The best technology tutorials, decided by you.</h3>
<p class="home-paragraph">
  tuutorials is a side-project of mine that really aims to make it easy to find great
  technology tutorials and get on with learning cool new stuff. Finding the best resources for
  learning something new sometimes requires a bit of time, so tuutorials puts them all
  in one place, making your life a little bit more efficient.
</p>

<h3 class="sub-heading">Submit. Vote. Review. Learn.</h3>
<p class="home-paragraph">
  You can try out submitted tutorials right now! Check out the technology list
  below to get things started. By
  <%= link_to "signing up", :new_user_registration %> you can submit 
  tutorials, vote for them and add reviews to the ones you have something to say about.
</p>

<h3 class="sub-heading">Something missing?</h3>
<p class="home-paragraph">
  Cool new technologies are always popping up, so I could really use your help keeping up.
  If you spot something missing that you think should make the list send me an 
  <%= mail_to "tuutorials@gmail.com", "email" %> and I'll add it as soon as I can.
</p>

<h2 id="technologies-heading">Technologies</h2>

<div id="nav-container">
  <ul id="nav-list">
    
    <% ("A".."Z").each do |letter| %>
      <li class="nav-item" onclick=$('#<%= letter %>').goTo();>
        <%= letter %>
      </li>
    <% end %>
    <li class="nav-item" onclick=$('#numbers').goTo();>0-9</li>
    <li class="nav-item" onclick=$('#symbols').goTo();>!?#</li>
    
  </ul>
</div>

<ul id="technology-list">

  <!-- Technologies that start with a letter -->
  <% ("A".."Z").each do |letter| %>
    <h3 class="letter" id="<%= letter %>"><%= letter %></h3>
    <% if !@groupedAlphabetically[letter].nil? %>
      <% @groupedAlphabetically[letter].each do |technology| %>
        <li class="technology-item"><%= link_to technology.name, technology %></li>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>

  <!-- Technologies that start with a number -->
  <h3 class="letter" id="numbers">0-9</h3>
  <% ("0".."9").each do |number| %>
    <% if !@groupedAlphabetically[number].nil? %>
      <% @groupedAlphabetically[number].each do |technology| %>
        <li class="technology-item"><%= link_to technology.name, technology %></li>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>

  <!-- Technologies that start with a symbol -->
  <h3 class="letter" id="symbols">!?#</h3>
  <!-- TODO -->

</ul>